{"tid":919760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[滾滾來] 疑爭用廚房起爭執 天水圍媳婦熱水淋家姑被捕","createTime":"2018-11-28T09:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T13:39:59.000Z","uid":1735,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"394216225871d6c9ce0e793873361d9f7fbd42a9","tid":919760,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:47:56.000Z","msg":"早上8時許，天水圍天晴邨晴悅樓1個單位發生1宗傷人案，28歲姓吳媳婦與59歲姓陳家姑，懷疑因為爭廚房而起爭執，媳婦情緒激動向家姑淋潑熱水。<br />\n25歲姓梁男子發現事件後馬上報警，警方及救護員接報到場，以涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害為由拘捕媳婦，並將腹部受傷的家姑送天水圍醫院治理，警方正就事件展開調查。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e7%96%91%e7%88%ad%e7%94%a8%e5%bb%9a%e6%88%bf%e8%b5%b7%e7%88%ad%e5%9f%b7-%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%b4%e5%9c%8d%e5%aa%b3%e5%a9%a6%e7%86%b1%e6%b0%b4%e6%b7%8b%e5%ae%b6%e5%a7%91%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95-151762\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25e7%2596%2591%25e7%2588%25ad%25e7%2594%25a8%25e5%25bb%259a%25e6%2588%25bf%25e8%25b5%25b7%25e7%2588%25ad%25e5%259f%25b7-%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e5%259c%258d%25e5%25aa%25b3%25e5%25a9%25a6%25e7%2586%25b1%25e6%25b0%25b4%25e6%25b7%258b%25e5%25ae%25b6%25e5%25a7%2591%25e8%25a2%25ab%25e6%258d%2595-151762&d=%2BWpD9ZlUq4iJirSvHYEh%2BL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=e58a390d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%e7%96%91%e7%88%ad%e7%94%a8%e5%bb%9a%e6%88%bf%e8%b5%b7%e7%88%ad%e5%9f%b7-%e5%a4%a9%e6%b0%b4%e5%9c%8d%e5%aa%b3%e5%a9%a6%e7%86%b1%e6%b0%b4%e6%b7%8b%e5%ae%b6%e5%a7%91%e8%a2%ab%e6%8d%95-151762</a><br />\n<br />\n媳婦使用熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 效果很有效"},{"pid":"db5df6277dc6eda4cd04b9da17f77a7a11c9693f","tid":919760,"uid":1735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:50:40.000Z","msg":"究竟嘈咩可以去到淋滾水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8423f6c9a2a5f9cc7b5f37fe57c113b649ab2026","tid":919760,"uid":199692,"like":2,"dislike":0,"scor